cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.AI. 

The paper proposes a method for material recognition using deep representations of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves feature selection and integration, which falls under the category of machine learning, specifically in the areas of deep learning and transfer learning. Hence, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a likely category. The paper also deals with measuring uncertainty and entropy, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves the use of CNNs, which is a popular technique in the field of artificial intelligence, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a possible category as well.
